Some might say that
to be here gathered today

6
00:01:05,588 --> 00:01:10,321
to mourn the loss of a car
would be going too far.

7
00:01:28,711 --> 00:01:35,173
<i>In 1996, electric cars began to appear
on roads all over California.</i>

8
00:01:36,218 --> 00:01:38,345
<i>They were quiet and fast,</i>

9
00:01:38,421 --> 00:01:42,380
<i>produced no exhaust
and ran without gasoline.</i>

10
00:01:42,858 --> 00:01:47,818
<i>Ten years later, these futuristic
cars were almost entirely gone.</i>

11
00:01:50,299 --> 00:01:51,630
<i>What happened?</i>

12
00:01:51,701 --> 00:01:55,899
<i>Why should we be haunted
by the ghost of the electric car?</i>

13
00:01:59,375 --> 00:02:02,867
<i>This wasn't the first time
the electric car was killed.</i>

14
00:02:03,112 --> 00:02:06,775
<i>One hundred years ago,
