15
00:02:06,849 --> 00:02:08,976
<i>than there were gas cars.</i>

16
00:02:09,418 --> 00:02:12,819
<i>For many people electric
cars were the car of choice.</i>

17
00:02:13,422 --> 00:02:17,290
<i>They were quiet an smooth,
and could be charged at home.</i>

18
00:02:18,561 --> 00:02:22,964
<i>Gas cars by comparison required
cranking and produced exhaust.</i>

19
00:02:25,401 --> 00:02:28,768
I'm so old I remember electric cars,

20
00:02:29,905 --> 00:02:31,270
when they were around in the beginning.

21
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:34,935
<i>I would've been about six years old
on the way to the symphony</i>

22
00:02:35,011 --> 00:02:37,844
<i>in that darling little electric car.</i>

23
00:02:38,314 --> 00:02:42,808
<i>They were very quiet, and it
had beveled glass windows.</i>

24
00:02:43,085 --> 00:02:47,078
It was almost like
sitting inside a huge lamp.

25
00:02:48,958 --> 00:02:50,220
<i>What happened?</i>

26
00:02:50,292 --> 00:02:54,353
<i>Why did the gas car win
over the electric car?</i>

27
00:02:54,864 --> 00:02:57,731
<i>As the 20th century gathered speed,</i>

28
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,234
<i>the electric car lost momentum.</i>

29
00:03:00,436 --> 00:03:04,065
<i>Automatic starters, cheaper
oil and mass production</i>

30
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:06,768
<i>gave the edge to the gasoline car.</i>

31
00:03:07,610 --> 00:03:11,876
<i>By 1920, the internal combustion
engine had won the race</i>

32
00:03:11,947 --> 00:03:13,437
<i>for control of the roads.</i>

33
00:03:13,883 --> 00:03:17,080
<i>And the modern automobile age was born.</i>

34
00:03:26,095 --> 00:03:29,826
<i>Of the hundreds of millions
of cars built in the 20th century,</i>

35
00:03:29,899 --> 00:03:31,799
<i>almost none were electric.</i>

36
00:03:33,102 --> 00:03:36,128
<i>They were sleek.
They were fast.</i>

37
00:03:36,205 --> 00:03:39,299
<i>And they gave Americans the open road.</i>

38
00:03:40,676 --> 00:03:45,204
<i>But as time went on, their
number one flaw became apparent.</i>

39
00:03:48,017 --> 00:03:49,416
<i>Smog.</i>

40
00:03:59,929 --> 00:04:02,693
<i>California has the worst
air quality in the nation.</i>

41
00:04:02,765 --> 00:04:06,166
