47
00:04:26,989 --> 00:04:29,856
<i>In 1989, a study found</i>

48
00:04:29,925 --> 00:04:34,624
<i>that one out of four 15 to 25
year-olds in Los Angeles county</i>

49
00:04:34,697 --> 00:04:39,031
<i>had severe lung lesions
