50
00:04:39,301 --> 00:04:43,829
<i>In 1990, there were 41
stage one smog alerts.</i>

51
00:04:45,574 --> 00:04:47,906
<i>No matter what kind of car we drive,</i>

52
00:04:47,977 --> 00:04:50,036
<i>every gallon of gas we burn,</i>

