and CO2 is a global warming gas.

58
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:15,727
<i>I believe the problems of
global warming will be far greater</i>

59
00:05:15,805 --> 00:05:17,167
than the problems of social security

60
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,901
or even the problems of war on terrorism.

61
00:05:20,943 --> 00:05:24,379
<i>We've got the equivalent of a nuclear time bomb</i>

62
00:05:24,446 --> 00:05:27,142
<i>on our hand,
