The Sunraycer was a solar-powered vehicle
that was developed here, at AeroVironment,

78
00:06:27,176 --> 00:06:28,939
for the purpose of winning a race.

79
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:34,413
<i>In 1987, GM won the World Solar
Challenge race in Australia</i>

80
00:06:34,550 --> 00:06:39,112
<i>with a one-of-a-kind solar-powered
electric vehicle, the Sunraycer.</i>

81
00:06:39,188 --> 00:06:43,591
<i>Emboldened by their success,
