00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:27,726
<i>unlike any that had
ever been driven before.</i>

94
00:07:31,774 --> 00:07:35,733
They've kept this car also a secret,
much better than any Detroit secret

95
00:07:36,913 --> 00:07:38,712
