106
00:08:13,015 --> 00:08:14,073
It was interesting.

107
00:08:15,217 --> 00:08:17,651
Program manager called me and said:

108
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,847
"Would you like to be on the
electric vehicle program?"

109
