116
00:08:43,178 --> 00:08:47,376
It caught the attention of the
California Air Resources Board.

117
00:08:47,983 --> 00:08:50,281
<i>California's Air Resources Board,</i>

118
00:08:50,953 --> 00:08:52,442
<i>or CARB as it was known,</i>

119
00:08:52,521 --> 00:08:56,958
