125
00:09:13,442 --> 00:09:16,741
<i>Knowing a modern electric
car was now possible,</i>

126
00:09:16,812 --> 00:09:20,839
<i>California regulators took a bold
and unprecedented step.</i>

127
00:09:20,916 --> 00:09:24,181
<i>They passed the Zero Emissions Vehicle mandate.</i>

128
00:09:24,319 --> 00:09:25,843
<i>The mandate was simple.</i>

129
00:09:25,921 --> 00:09:30,221
<i>If automakers wanted to
continue to sell cars in California,</i>

130
00:09:30,459 --> 00:09:34,418
