134
00:09:41,703 --> 00:09:44,934
<i>For the car companies there
were only two options;</i>

135
00:09:45,007 --> 00:09:47,373
<i>Comply with the law or fight it.</i>

136
00:09:48,077 --> 00:09:50,568
<i>In the end, they would do both.</i>

137
00:10:07,629 --> 00:10:11,690
