412
00:26:12,527 --> 00:26:15,826
<i>to commercialize the
fuel cell for cars and buses.</i>

413
00:26:16,431 --> 00:26:17,955
<i>Soon you may see some of these cars</i>

414
00:26:18,032 --> 00:26:20,296
<i>cruising through your
very own neighborhood.</i>

415
00:26:20,368 --> 00:26:23,235
<i>We will not just dream about
the hydrogen fuelling stations.</i>

416
00:26:23,672 --> 00:26:27,066
<i>We will not just dream about the
