418
00:26:31,712 --> 00:26:35,170
<i>It's a way for governor
Schwarzenegger to have a property</i>

419
00:26:35,249 --> 00:26:37,410
<i>at various events that ge
goes to when he unveils</i>

420
00:26:37,485 --> 00:26:41,114
a new hydrogen refuelling station.
At LAX for example.

421
00:26:41,589 --> 00:26:44,922
<i>I am going to encourage the
building of a hydrogen highway</i>

422
00:26:44,992 --> 00:26:47,586
<i>to take us to the
environmental future.</i>

423
00:26:47,728 --> 00:26:52,688
<i>While hydrogen fuel cells offered an exciting
