run your wires down.

1325
01:26:13,824 --> 01:26:15,655
Everything is plug-and-play.

1326
01:26:16,594 --> 01:26:20,428
Anybody that wants to make a
revolution shouldn't grab a gun.

1327
01:26:20,731 --> 01:26:23,859
Just go and start
working like we do

1328
01:26:23,934 --> 01:26:27,267
to change the world by
using science and technology.

1329
01:26:29,674 --> 01:26:31,403
I am so optimistic about the future.

1330
01:26:31,475 --> 01:26:34,842
Even given everything that we've
seen, and all of the EV wars,

1331
01:26:34,912 --> 01:26:36,436
I remain an optimist.

1332
01:26:37,615 --> 01:26:39,879
<i>One of the things that makes America work</i>

