1336
01:26:53,131 --> 01:26:55,259
<i>And here we have a serious problem:</i>

1337
01:26:55,332 --> 01:26:57,391
<i>America is addicted to oil.</i>

1338
01:26:57,468 --> 01:27:00,835
I call all this a potential coalition
between the tree-huggers,

1339
01:27:00,905 --> 01:27:04,636
